<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Workshop Game Development</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1c2c, #5d275d);
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 126, 95, 0.2);
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #d1d1d1;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
      color: #fff;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    
    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      width: 220px;
      text-align: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #feb47b;
    }
    
    footer {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Workshop Game Development</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Belajar membuat game dari dasar hingga mahir dengan instruktur profesional</p>
      
      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="/participants/create" class="btn btn-primary">Daftar Sekarang</a>
        <a href="/participants" class="btn btn-secondary">Lihat Peserta</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">ðŸŽ®</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Unity 3D</h3>
        <p>Belajar membuat game 3D dengan engine populer Unity</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">ðŸš€</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Unreal Engine</h3>
        <p>Kembangkan game dengan kualitas grafis tinggi</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">ðŸ‘¾</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Godot Engine</h3>
        <p>Engine open-source untuk pengembangan game multiplatform</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">ðŸŽ¨</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Game Art & Design</h3>
        <p>Desain karakter, environment, dan UI untuk game</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
      &copy; 2025 Workshop Game Development. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>